      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:39:1",
      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ حَدُّ النَّبَّاشِ حَدُّ السَّارِقِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibraahim, from his father and Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Al Fazl Bin Shazaan, altogether from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hafs Bin Al Bakhtary who said, ",
          "‘I heard Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> saying: ‘Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the grave robber is the Penalty (Hadd) of the thief’."
        ]
      }
